= Tor Upstream Unfixed Denial of Service Issue =

Tor upstream DoS issue [https://gitlab.torproject.org/tpo/core/tor/-/work_items/26294 attacker can force intro point rotation by ddos] was reported by Tor developer [https://gitlab.torproject.org/arma Roger Dingledine]. At the time of writing:

* Issue opened in <code>2018</code>.
* <code>Status</code>: <code>Open</code>, <code>Not Scheduled</code>.
* [https://gitlab.torproject.org/tpo/core/tor/-/work_items/26294#note_2907391 Last comment by Roger Dingledine in <code>2023</code>].
* Last ticket status change to <code>Not Scheduled</code> in December <code>2025</code>.

