Arti's Vanguards implementation is based on the research behind Tor's [https://blog.torproject.org/announcing-vanguards-add-onion-services/ Vanguards add-on], and offers similar protections to its [https://github.com/mikeperry-tor/vanguards/blob/master/README_TECHNICAL.md#the-vanguards-subsystem Vanguards component].
